replies.txt_content:
/give @s minecraft:diamond_helmet 1 0 {special:1b}
/give @s minecraft:diamond_chestplate 1 0 {special:1b}
/give @s minecraft:diamond_leggings 1 0 {special:1b}
/give @s minecraft:diamond_boots 1 0 {special:1b}
以上是给予特殊装备的命令。如果想加附魔、自定义名称等，保留 special 不动，直接拿逗号隔开加在后面就行了。例如：
/give @s minecraft:diamond_helmet 1 0 {special:1b,display:{Name:"名字"}}

以下是检测特殊装备的命令：
scoreboard players tag remove @a special
scoreboard players tag add @a special {Inventory:[{Slot:100b,tag:{special:1b}},{Slot:101b,tag:{special:1b}},{Slot:102b,tag:{special:1b}},{Slot:103b,tag:{special:1b}}]}
say 穿着特殊装备的玩家：@a[tag=special]
